About Me!
My name is Brooke, and I am a graduate student in the Masters of Geomatics for Environmental Management (MGEM) programâ€™s class of 2025. Originally from Ethiopia, Canada has been my home for the past seven years. I am pursuing the MGEM to deepen my understanding of geomatics concepts and tools, develop new technical and analytically skills, and enhance my qualifications for a career in environmental and resource management.
